Frizzy hair is one or the most common problems out there. No matter how much serum we apply, it will be frizzy again. Frizzy hair is not necessarily genetics, heat styling, over washing, not oiling regularly etc. are some of the reasons of it.

Therefore the hair needs to be hydrated from within in order to get rid of it. For this I have a routine that would help you too.

✨Oil your hair length along with scalp regularly. Especially before taking head bath.

✨Use a hydrating shampoo & conditioner/mask like this one from @bbluntindia
The intense moisture range has great moisturising properties as it contains jojoba oil & Vitamin E.

Jojoba Oil is rich in vitamins and minerals, so it acts as a natural moisturizer thatnourishes and strengthens hair while imparting shine.

Vitamin E is a great ingredient for Hair as it hydrates and rejuvenates dry and flaky scalp. It also boosts hair elasticity and shine while promoting growth.
